= Montage workflow Rakefile

* Prepare Input files
 * r/*.fits
 * r/region.hdr
 * r/shrunk.hdr

* Edit options

 $ vi pwrake_conf.yaml
 $ vi hosts
 $ vi params.rb

* Prepare Initial files

 $ rake -f Rakefile.prepare

* Run Pwrake

 $ pwrake

* Run Pwrake

 $ rake -f Rakefile.clean clean
 $ rake -f Rakefile.clean clobber
